snippet.title: Dust&Courage: Jake Bolton's Journey - Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
The big day is here, and we couldn’t be more excited! After nearly a year of hard work, we’re finally ready to share what we’ve been working on with you. We’re thrilled to introduce Jake’s Journey and can’t wait to see the choices you make as you shape the game. The free demo is now available on Steam, we hope you enjoy it!

Play the free demo: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3128930/Dust__Courage_Jake_Boltons_Journey_Demo/
